While your workout should be intense, getting out of your workout pants into something a bit more comfortable shouldn't be. Not every gym session, long run, strenuous hike, or vinyasa class requires a pair of tight-fitting leggings. Sometimes we just want to wear something comfy that can easily go from the studio to the street. See below for our favorite workout pants that could pass as real pants: HuffPost may receive a share from purchases made via links on this page.